videos.headline: 290-lb FB McMorris gives Cal lead with TD catch
videos.description: Chase Garbers baits the defense with a play-action fake, then finds a wide-open Malik McMorris in the end zone to give the Golden Bears a 7-3 lead over the Cougars.

videos.headline: Borghi keeps feet moving to give Cougars lead
videos.description: RB Max Borghi pushes the pile and muscles his way across the goal line for a 5-yard touchdown run, making it 10-7 Cougars.

videos.headline: Washington State blows pick-6 with fumble at 3-yard line
videos.description: Willie Taylor III nearly goes for a 40-yard pick-6, but QB Chase Garbers makes up for his mistake by causing the fumble, which goes out of the end zone for a touchback.

videos.headline: McIlwain throws costly red zone INT
videos.description: With the Golden Bears threatening to take the lead, Brandon McIlwain throws away the drive as Skyler Thomas picks him off in the end zone.

videos.headline: Minshew tosses game-winning 10-yard TD
videos.description: Gardner Minshew makes a beautiful throw to WR Easop Winston, who hauls it in for the go-ahead touchdown with just 32 seconds to play.
